originalText.text:
Moises Farhat has been my go to person for all management issues in my Upper Westside cooperative in NYC for the last five years - ever since I bought it.

His knowledge, intelligence, responsiveness, execution and customer care has been phenomenal. I have had interactions with property management companies in New York for the better part of fifty years and find him exceptional.

As a prior Board Member of a Greenwich Village coop I know good Property Management when I see it in action.

I recommend Moises and his team at Farhat Realty Management very strongly.  You will be happy to have him on your side.

originalText.text: Moises Farhat has been the managing agent for my cooperative building in Morningside Heights for nearly three decades now. Throughout all these years, he has always been responsive and eager to resolve my concerns and problems as quickly as possible. They've been on top of our finances, NYC compliance and capital improvements. Their customer service is impeccable. His knowledge and experience truly shine. I'd certainly recommend his company to anyone in need of management services.

originalText.text: I leased my apartment from Farhat for almost three years. They were a wonderful landlord the entire time, and took great care of the building I lived at. They were super helpful and responsive with all of the issues that came up over the term of our tenancy, and even made some requested  improvements to our apartment when we resigned our lease - new vanity and medicine cabinet. Would definitely recommend!
